  "title": "Hostess",
  "description": "<p>Key Responsibilities</p><p>* Guest Welcome: Greet guests warmly, confirm reservations, and provide accurate wait times.</p><p>* Seating Management: Efficiently seat parties at appropriate tables, managing table turnover.</p><p>* Reservations: Handle bookings, cancellations, and inquiries via phone, online, or in-person.</p><p>* Coordination: Communicate with servers and kitchen staff to manage guest flow.</p><p>* Customer Service: Address guest feedback and issues, ensuring a pleasant dining atmosphere.</p><p>* Front-of-House: Keep the entrance area clean, organized, and welcoming. Essential Skills & Qualities</p><p>* Customer Service: Friendly, welcoming, and patient demeanor.• Communication: Clear and effective verbal skills.</p><p></p><p>* Organization & Multitasking: Managing multiple tasks and guests simultaneously.</p><p>* Teamwork: Ability to work effectively with the service staff.</p><p>* Professionalism: Calmness under pressure and a polished appearance.</p><p>* Technical Skills: Familiarity with reservation systems (e.g., OpenTable).</p><p></p><p>Requirements• Motivational and  Positive attitude.</p>",
